webpackJsonp([85981566840613],{793:function(a,e){a.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<p>Program metrics show how healthy a program is. They enable hackers to see various statistics regarding:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Program information</li>\n<li>Response efficiency</li>\n<li>Bounty statistics</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The metrics are displayed on the right side of the program\'s security page.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/program-metrics-346abb3bf569b32ce37f1a825ff8c056-08d2d.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 86.96517412935324%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Program metrics"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/program-metrics-346abb3bf569b32ce37f1a825ff8c056-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/program-metrics-346abb3bf569b32ce37f1a825ff8c056-67829.png 125w,\n/static/program-metrics-346abb3bf569b32ce37f1a825ff8c056-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/program-metrics-346abb3bf569b32ce37f1a825ff8c056-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/program-metrics-346abb3bf569b32ce37f1a825ff8c056-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/program-metrics-346abb3bf569b32ce37f1a825ff8c056-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/program-metrics-346abb3bf569b32ce37f1a825ff8c056-08d2d.png 1005w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>Displaying Program Metrics</h3>\n<p>To display program metrics on your security page:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to your program\'s <strong>Settings > Programs > Customization > Metrics Display</strong>.</li>\n<li>Select the statistics you want to display on your security page.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Update</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/program-metrics-2-61551bfd69c0658b42dd5e01b8c2c15c-e4b13.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 63.77870563674322%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Program metrics-2"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/program-metrics-2-61551bfd69c0658b42dd5e01b8c2c15c-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/program-metrics-2-61551bfd69c0658b42dd5e01b8c2c15c-67829.png 125w,\n/static/program-metrics-2-61551bfd69c0658b42dd5e01b8c2c15c-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/program-metrics-2-61551bfd69c0658b42dd5e01b8c2c15c-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/program-metrics-2-61551bfd69c0658b42dd5e01b8c2c15c-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/program-metrics-2-61551bfd69c0658b42dd5e01b8c2c15c-e4b13.png 958w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>Response Efficiency Metrics</h3>\n<p>Response efficiency metrics include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Average time to first response</li>\n<li>Average time to triage</li>\n<li>Average time to resolution</li>\n<li>Average time to bounty\nThe averages are calculated by the last 90 days. These metrics give hackers a better idea of how responsive a program is.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Bounty Statistics</h3>\n<p>Bounty metrics are calculated over a programâ€™s lifetime and set realistic expectations with hackers and security teams. You can view:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Total bounties paid</li>\n<li>Average bounty (Displayed as a range from the 45th to 55th percentile)</li>\n<li>Top bounty (Displayed as a range from the 90th to 100th percentile)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Total bounties paid can be a strong indicator that a bounty program is active and healthy. The mean and median bounty also serve as rough guidance for how much a hacker can expect in return for a valid report.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><i>Note: Any reports filed by a security team\'s members will not be reflected in the metrics.</i></p>\n</blockquote>',frontmatter:{path:"/programs/program-metrics.html",id:"programs/program-metrics",title:"Program Metrics",description:null}}},pathContext:{}}}});
